msgctxt "100_Hana"
msgid "Chief..."
msgstr "Jefe..."

msgctxt "112_Akiyama"
msgid "He's made his decision. It's not my place to interfere."
msgstr "Ha tomado su decisión. No me corresponde interferir."

msgctxt "124_Hana"
msgid "But... becoming a loan shark, of all things."
msgstr "Pero... hacerse prestamista, entre tantas opciones..."

msgctxt "136_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, he probably has his reasons."
msgstr "Quién sabe. Debe tener sus motivos."

msgctxt "148_Hana"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "160_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm more concerned about our new customer. He should be here by now."
msgstr "Ahora mismo estoy más preocupado por el nuevo cliente. Ya debería haber llegado."

msgctxt "172_Hana"
msgid "You're right. He said he was nearby."
msgstr "Tiene razón. Dijo que estaba cerca."

msgctxt "220_Hana"
msgid "Hello, this is Sky Finance."
msgstr "Hola, Sky Finance al habla."

msgctxt "232_Potential Client"
msgid "Hi, yes, I called a little while ago..."
msgstr "Hola, sí, llamé hace un rato..."

msgctxt "244_Potential Client"
msgid "A young man outside your building offered to talk with me\\r\n"\n"and took me over to a different office."
msgstr "Un joven afuera de su edificio se acercó a hablarme\\r\n"\n"y me llevó a una oficina diferente."

msgctxt "256_Hana"
msgid "One moment, please."
msgstr "Un momento, por favor."

msgctxt "268_Hana"
msgid "Chief? It's the customer who called earlier. It sounds like\\r\n"\n"Shiobara-san got to him..."
msgstr "Jefe, es el cliente que llamó antes.\\r\n"\n"Parece que Shiobara-san se lo llevó..."

msgctxt "316_Akiyama"
msgid "Hello, Akiyama speaking. You were saying something about a\\r\n"\n"young man outside my office?"
msgstr "Buenas, aquí el jefe. Cómo es eso de que lo llevaron a otra\\r\n"\n"oficina."

msgctxt "328_Potential Client"
msgid "Oh, uh, that's right. I humored the young man with what he\\r\n"\n"had to say, but I still wanted to stop by your place."
msgstr "Ah, así es. Es que le seguí la corriente a ese joven,\\r\n"\n"pero aún quiero pasarme por tu oficina."

msgctxt "340_Potential Client"
msgid "So now I'm calling you from his office restroom..."
msgstr "Ahora mismo te estoy llamando desde el baño del lugar..."

msgctxt "352_Akiyama"
msgid "Any chance you can just turn him down and leave?"
msgstr "¿No puedes simplemente decirle que no e irte?"

msgctxt "364_Potential Client"
msgid "Well... I feel like he's going to pressure me into signing\\r\n"\n"something."
msgstr "Es que, siento que me va a obligar a firmar un contrato\\r\n"\n"o algo así."

msgctxt "376_Akiyama"
msgid "All right. Wait right there. Where is this office?"
msgstr "Entiendo. Espera allí. ¿Dónde está la oficina?"

msgctxt "388_Potential Client"
msgid "Um, I think it's right near the M Store. It's a white\\r\n"\n"building."
msgstr "Veamos, creo que está cerca de la M Store.\\r\n"\n"Es un edificio blanco."

msgctxt "400_Akiyama"
msgid "Near the M Store? Okay, hang tight－and don't sign anything."
msgstr "¿Cerca de la M Store? Por favor, espérame en el lugar y no firmes nada."

msgctxt "436_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay, I'll be back."
msgstr "Es hora de irme."

msgctxt "472_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey there."
msgstr "Buenas, buenas."

msgctxt "496_Hana"
msgid "Hello, Chief. You're back late."
msgstr "Bienvenido de nuevo, jefe. Llega tarde."

msgctxt "508_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, well..."
msgstr "Un poquito..."

msgctxt "520_Hana"
msgid "Hmm, what have you been up to...? Anyway, did you hear the rumors?"
msgstr "Muy sospechoso... Cambiando de tema, ¿escuchó los rumores?"

msgctxt "532_Akiyama"
msgid "Rumors?"
msgstr "¿Rumores?"

msgctxt "544_Hana"
msgid "About Shiobara-san. The man you lent five million yen to?"
msgstr "Acerca de Shiobara-san.\n"\n"El hombre al que le prestó cinco millones de yenes."

msgctxt "556_Akiyama"
msgid "What about him?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con él?"

msgctxt "568_Hana"
msgid "Apparently, Shiobara-san is really coming up in the world\\r\n"\n"these days."
msgstr "Aparentemente a Shiobara-san le está yendo muy bien\\r\n"\n"últimamente."

msgctxt "580_Akiyama"
msgid "Is this the same Shiobara?"
msgstr "¿Hablamos del mismo Shiobara?"

msgctxt "592_Shiobara"
msgid "Hello!"
msgstr "¡Hola!"

msgctxt "604_Akiyama"
msgid "Speak of the devil."
msgstr "Hablando del rey de roma."

msgctxt "616_Shiobara"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

msgctxt "628_Akiyama"
msgid "Never mind. Please, have a seat."
msgstr "Olvida eso. Por favor, toma asiento."

msgctxt "640_Shiobara"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "Gracias."

msgctxt "700_Akiyama"
msgid "So, did you figure out what you want to do?"
msgstr "¿Y terminaste encontrando lo que querías hacer?"

msgctxt "712_Shiobara"
msgid "I did. I'm going to work in finance, just like you."
msgstr "Así es. También trabajaré en el mundo de las finanzas, igual que usted."

msgctxt "724_Akiyama"
msgid "You want to do finance?"
msgstr "¿Vas a dedicarte a las finanzas?"

msgctxt "736_Shiobara"
msgid "You've been a big influence, of course."
msgstr "Sí, usted ha sido una gran influencia para mí."

msgctxt "748_Shiobara"
msgid "But, more than that, I'd once faced money troubles of my\\r\n"\n"own."
msgstr "Además, también enfrenté problemas económicos."

msgctxt "760_Shiobara"
msgid "I decided I wanted to do something involving money－as a way\\r\n"\n"of overcoming my own problems, too."
msgstr "Por eso me gustaría hacer algo que involucre dinero.\\r\n"\n"Cómo forma de superar mis propios problemas."

msgctxt "772_Akiyama"
msgid "You don't say..."
msgstr "No me digas..."

msgctxt "784_Shiobara"
msgid "So I started out like you did, Akiyama-san, and did some\\r\n"\n"day-trading."
msgstr "Así que empecé igualito a usted, Akiyama-san,\\r\n"\n"con algo de day trading."

msgctxt "796_Akiyama"
msgid "You were a day-trader?"
msgstr "¿Hiciste day trading?"

msgctxt "808_Shiobara"
msgid "Uh-huh. You need money to work in finance, so I made the\\r\n"\n"most of your advice."
msgstr "Ajá. Se necesita dinero para trabajar en finanzas,\\r\n"\n"así que seguí sus consejos."

msgctxt "820_Akiyama"
msgid "I don't think I really told you anything all that useful,\\r\n"\n"but okay."
msgstr "No creo haber dicho algo suficientemente útil\\r\n"\n"como para ser considerado un consejo."

msgctxt "832_Shiobara"
msgid "Well, I did plenty of studying on my own, too. To tell you\\r\n"\n"the truth, I've never pushed myself so hard in all my life."
msgstr "Bueno, también estudié muchísimo por mi cuenta.\\r\n"\n"La verdad, nunca me había esforzado tanto en mí vida."

msgctxt "844_Shiobara"
msgid "Maybe the effort paid off, or maybe I was just good at it,\\r\n"\n"but that five million yen grew and grew. I've amassed a\\r\n"\n"sizable sum, if I do say so myself."
msgstr "No sé si los esfuerzos dieron resultados o si tenía talento\\r\n"\n"para ello, pero los cinco millones siguieron creciendo\\r\n"\n"y creciendo. Y ahora tengo una suma considerable."

msgctxt "856_Shiobara"
msgid "Granted, it's not as much as you have!"
msgstr "¡Pero de seguro no es nada comparado a lo que tiene Akiyama-san!"

msgctxt "868_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "880_Shiobara"
msgid "I thought I'd come by today and return the money you lent\\r\n"\n"me..."
msgstr "Y es por eso que hoy, he venido a devolverte el dinero\\r\n"\n"que me prestaste..."

msgctxt "892_Shiobara"
msgid "To that end, I've prepared ten million yen."
msgstr "Y para ello he preparado diez millones de yenes."

msgctxt "904_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm sure we agreed I wouldn't charge you any interest."
msgstr "Estoy seguro de que acordamos un préstamo sin intereses."

msgctxt "916_Shiobara"
msgid "No, I just want to express my gratitude."
msgstr "No es eso, es que quiero expresar mi gratitud."

msgctxt "928_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, I'm only taking five million."
msgstr "De todas formas, sólo tomaré cinco millones."

msgctxt "940_Shiobara"
msgid "...I see."
msgstr "...Ya veo."

msgctxt "988_Shiobara"
msgid "Consider this as thanks for all your help."
msgstr "Considera esto un agradecimiento por toda su ayuda."

msgctxt "1000_Hana"
msgid "But I didn't do anything. I really can't accept this."
msgstr "Pero yo no hice nada. No puedo aceptarlo..."

msgctxt "1012_Shiobara"
msgid "Oh, go on. Take it."
msgstr "Oh, vamos. Tómalo."

msgctxt "1072_Akiyama"
msgid "...You've really changed."
msgstr "...Realmente has cambiado."

msgctxt "1084_Shiobara"
msgid "I took the money you lent me and fought like hell to make\\r\n"\n"it grow, all in the hopes of truly changing my life for the\\r\n"\n"better."
msgstr "Tomé el dinero que me prestó y me esforcé como loco\\r\n"\n"para hacerlo crecer, todo con la esperanza de cambiar\\r\n"\n"mi vida para mejor."

msgctxt "1096_Shiobara"
msgid "I believed in what you told me－that if I proved I was\\r\n"\n"serious, people would be happy to work with me."
msgstr "Creí en lo que me dijiste: si demostraba que iba en serio,\\r\n"\n"la gente estaría encantada de trabajar conmigo."

msgctxt "1108_Shiobara"
msgid "It was the first time I'd really applied myself like that."
msgstr "Es la primera vez que doy todo de mí."

msgctxt "1120_Shiobara"
msgid "And before I knew it, everything was different－the world\\r\n"\n"around me and everyone in it."
msgstr "Y antes de darme cuenta, todo había cambiado.\\r\n"\n"El entorno y las personas."

msgctxt "1132_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1144_Shiobara"
msgid "At first I thought, \"Wow, Akiyama-san was right after all.\""
msgstr "Al principio pensé: \"Wow, Akiyama-san tenía razón después de todo\"."

msgctxt "1156_Shiobara"
msgid "But then I gradually came to understand that the reason\\r\n"\n"those around me were so accommodating wasn't that I was\\r\n"\n"making such an earnest effort."
msgstr "Pero poco a poco empecé a entender de que las personas\\r\n"\n"que me rodeaban no estaban actuando así porque\\r\n"\n"fuese serio."

msgctxt "1168_Shiobara"
msgid "It was because I was successful and had money."
msgstr "Era porque tenia éxito y dinero."

msgctxt "1180_Shiobara"
msgid "That's when I realized something: in order to change\\r\n"\n"somebody's life, you need money."
msgstr "Fue entonces cuando me di cuenta de algo:\\r\n"\n"Para cambiar la vida de alguien, solo se necesita dinero."

msgctxt "1192_Shiobara"
msgid "That's why you can spur people into action, Akiyama-san.\\r\n"\n"You have money."
msgstr "La razón por la que Akiyama-san puede motivar a las personas,\\r\n"\n"es porque tiene dinero."

msgctxt "1204_Shiobara"
msgid "After all, it was your money that changed me."
msgstr "Después de todo, yo también pude cambiar gracias a tu dinero."

msgctxt "1216_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1228_Hana"
msgid "Akiyama-san..."
msgstr "Akiyama-san..."

msgctxt "1276_Hana"
msgid "Hello, this is Sky Finance."
msgstr "Hola, Sky Finance al habla."

msgctxt "1288_Potential Client"
msgid "Er, I was on my way over to your office, and I know I'm in\\r\n"\n"the right neighborhood..."
msgstr "Em, estaba de camino a su oficina, sé que ando bastante\\r\n"\n"cerca..."

msgctxt "1300_Potential Client"
msgid "...but I'm having a hard time finding it."
msgstr "...pero sigo sin encontrarla."

msgctxt "1312_Hana"
msgid "Where are you now?"
msgstr "¿Dónde está ahora?"

msgctxt "1324_Potential Client"
msgid "I'm under the Kamurocho gate. I can see a big sign for\\r\n"\n"Manzoku Sushi."
msgstr "Estoy bajo la puerta de Kamurocho. Puedo ver el cartel de\\r\n"\n"Sushi Manzoku."

msgctxt "1336_Hana"
msgid "Okay. Walk toward the sign, then go about 100 meters toward\\r\n"\n"the theater."
msgstr "Bueno, siga hacia el cartel, luego avance unos cien metros\\r\n"\n"en dirección al teatro."

msgctxt "1348_Hana"
msgid "The New Serena building will be on your left. We're on the\\r\n"\n"fifth floor."
msgstr "A su izquierda verá el edificio New Serena. La oficina se\\r\n"\n"encuentra en el quinto piso."

msgctxt "1360_Potential Client"
msgid "Got it. Thank you very much. I'll be right over."
msgstr "Lo tengo. Muchas gracias. Estaré por allá en un rato."

msgctxt "1396_Shiobara"
msgid "A new customer?"
msgstr "¿Un nuevo cliente?"

msgctxt "1408_Hana"
msgid "Sounds like it."
msgstr "Así parece."

msgctxt "1420_Shiobara"
msgid "As it just so happens, I've decided to be a moneylender here in Kamurocho myself."
msgstr "De hecho, también he decidido hacerme prestamista aquí en Kamurocho."

msgctxt "1432_Akiyama"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr "¿Qué...?"

msgctxt "1444_Hana"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1468_Shiobara"
msgid "I guess that means we'll be rivals. But what's business\\r\n"\n"without a little friendly competition? Well, I'd better be off."
msgstr "De ahora en adelante trabajaremos en el mismo sector.\\r\n"\n"Estoy ansioso de trabajar codo a codo. Ahora, si me disculpa."

